{{no footnotes|blp=yes|date=September 2017}}'''Zia Ahmed''' was a [[Pakistan]]i [[cricket]]er who played for Bahawalpur.

Ahmed made a single first-class appearance for the side, during the 1976-77 season, against Income Tax Department, in the BCCP Patrons Trophy. From the tailend, he scored a single run in the only innings in which he batted.

Ahmed bowled 8 overs in the match, taking figures of 0-52.

